{{Infobox company | company_name = 1010data, Inc. | company_logo = [[Image:1010data-logo.png]] | company_type = Private | foundation = 2000 | location = [[New York City|New York, NY]] | industry = [[Cloud computing]], [[Business analytics]], [[Database publishing]] | homepage = [http://www.1010data.com/ www.1010data.com] }}
'''1010data''' is a privately held company that provides a [[Cloud computing|cloud-based]] software platform and associated services for complex [[business analytics]] on and [[database publishing]] of very large data sets. The 1010data service is used in a variety of industries, including financial services, retail, consumer packaged goods, telecom, insurance, and others.<ref>Bloor, R.: "1010data offers a powerful columnar database", [http://www.thevirtualcircle.com/downloads/popular-downloads/?did=25] ''Big Data Analytics - This Time It's Personal'', May 23, 2011</ref>
